description.en:
PoW/PoS
SteepCoin uses a hybrid PoW/PoS system. This system creates a very strong blockchain and keeps transactions quick and fees very low. Also, being a hybrid coin, you get users that want to mine and stake instead of just one or the other.

Anonymity
Authentic Privacy: SteepCoin is dedicated to keeping your coins private by using advanced cryptographic protection features for your information. We'll continue to innovate.

Transactions
A service for instant transactions. In this system, the inputs are blocked only for a particular transaction that is verified by the consensus mechanism. Conflicting transactions are blocked and rejected. If a consensus can not be reached, the confirmation of the transaction occurs using the standard block confirmation mechanism.

Security
This system creates a very strong blockchain and keeps transactions quick and fees very low. Also, being a hybrid coin, you get users that want to mine and stake instead of just one or the other. This increases community support for the coin which increases demand.
